  "general_provisions": "This bill allows the State Board of Education (state board) to adjust funding for charter schools with significant enrollment underestimates.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet>provides the state board discretionary authority to allocate funds to adjust charter school enrollment estimates;<hr><ltbullet>specifies funding sources in priority order;<hr><ltbullet>requires reporting to the Office of the Legislative Fiscal Analyst and the Governor's Office of Planning and Budget; and<hr><ltbullet>exempts adjustments from certain budgetary requirements.",
